368994560429_7585562947056232922_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i1N-aS-KSIgQ7kNvgHGSzY1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB6mqlUNJJvxYqxsdp6_FWmc-ndpkv9jeXdRPX-C0YmiQ&oe=66E82028"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "VideoCover.png", "id": "490910340337703", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982706_490910343671036_2809014443838437620_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Q7WpfnjzRP4Q7kNvgF30A8R&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDR85YABKxsMPD2_wHv_jzyZnf2H51KGO8dctJBN0HxaA&oe=66E8188D"}, "display_name": "VRShootingRanges", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Enhances Reaction Speed and Focus: Due to the time-limited nature of the game, players need to quickly aim and shoot targets within the given timeframe, significantly improving reaction speed and focus.\n\nImproves Hand-Eye Coordination: The game requires players to maintain precise aim on moving targets, which greatly aids in enhancing hand-eye coordination.\n\nProvides a Safe Shooting Experience: Practicing shooting in a virtual environment allows players to experience the thrill and challenges of shooting while avoiding the potential risks associated with real-world shooting.\n\nGradual Skill Improvement: With the three different difficulty levels, players can gradually improve their shooting skills, allowing them to tackle more challenging scenarios.\n\nRelaxation and Stress Relief: The shooting game offers a way for players to relax, providing a temporary escape from the stresses of daily life by focusing on shooting targets.", "short_description": "This virtual shooting range game allows players to enhance their shooting skills in a safe environment. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://ecom.iscom.sg/index.php?route=information%2Finformation&language=en-gb&information_id=3", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "IS COM XR Apps Developer", "support_website_url": nul